research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for Holiday Lakes town, TX, include the Mayor and five Council Members. Information was gathered from the town's official website and other government directories. There was a minor discrepancy in the name for Position 1 (Roberta Carr vs. Joyce Carr) and Position 2 (Lorenzo Macias, Jr. vs. Lorenzo Macias) across different sources; the names from the Holiday Lakes town website and election information were prioritized for accuracy.
